						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying near the Sītārāmasvāmi temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Viḷambi, Śrāvaṇa, ba 10, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of a shrine and installation of the images of Sita, Rāma and Lakshmaṇa at Māchavaram by Kottamahālakshmi, the daughter of Ātukūri Kichchayya.</p>						

						</summary>
